title: Fathom Vol. 3 (2011 Digital Edition) (Darkness-Empire)
description:
Fathom Vol. 3: Worlds At War

English | CBR | 10 Issues

Genre: Fantasy, Science Fiction

Written by Written by J.T. Krul and Michael Turner
Art by Ale Garza

Collecting issues #1 through #10. The deadly tides of change rise above the surface in the exciting third chapter of FATHOM! Humankind faces a new threat to their existence from the ancient and powerful underwater race - the Black - while the return of the villainous Killian sends shockwaves throughout the already-devastated world of the Blue. Meanwhile, Aspen Matthews attempts to adjust to life above the water, but soon discovers that a future - and past - threat emerges to destroy her newly found safe haven!
